ComicInfo.Summary:
Unplugged, Part One: Joan remembers a gig twenty years earlier.
Brooklyn Blood, Chapter 3: O'Connor learns a plane had crashed decades earlier on the site where the murders are being found.
Chase the Lady, Chapter 5: Psykhe is involved in a shooting.
Chapter 6: Threshold Apprehension: Terripinians are chasing after Kyrra, Rollo, and Bazog.
Chapter 1, World Away: Kint is arrested.
Sundown Crossroads, Chapter 2: Katie has been possessed by the ghost of a lawyer.
